                    <Icon name='linkedin' size='huge' />
                    <Icon name='mail' size='huge' />

                </Segment>
                <Grid>
                    <Grid columns={3} relaxed='very' stackable>
                        <Grid.Column>

                        </Grid.Column>
                        <Grid.Column>

                        </Grid.Column>
                        <Grid.Column>

                        </Grid.Column>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Segment>
        </Container >
    )
};

export default Home;
